<body>
<h1>PMO Maturity Assessment Tool</h1>
<p>This tool allows you to assess the maturity of your PMO across multiple domains. Assign weights to domains, select the current maturity level for each capability, and generate a weighted maturity score with recommended next steps.</p>
<div id="weights-section">
  <h2>1. Domain Weighting</h2>
  <p>Assign a relative weight to each domain (default is equal). Weights will be normalised to sum to 1.</p>
  <table class="weights-table" id="weights-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Domain</th><th>Weight</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
<div id="assessment-section">
  <h2>2. Capabilities Assessment</h2>
